{"tid":2250273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"怕打仗！支那年輕人也逃兵！戶籍慘遭「永久備註」拒服兵役","createTime":"2020-10-20T03:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T04:34:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b4648b40489623f51a9bfe79c889ec7bc42aa7","tid":2250273,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gkTvudg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgkTvudg.jpg&h=78066189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在台灣當兵是公民應盡的義務，許多人也因此想方設法逃避當兵，不過就算是採取志願役<br />\n的中國，「逃兵」的狀況也是層出不窮。中國四川省近日爆出1名軍人經過一系列審核後，<br />\n順利入伍、分發到河北省一個空軍基地服役，不過他以各種不適應部隊生活為由，拒絕服<br />\n役，最後慘遭除名，還被當局認為「影響惡劣」，處以戶籍資料永久備註「拒服兵役」的<br />\n一系列處罰，被當局作為「反面典型」遭官媒報導，且近來至少發生3起類似案例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=833891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D833891&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=cf392286\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D833891&h=f6cd18f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=833891</a>"},{"pid":"882f92095d84c188ec95d0b6b47ddd8008ccd459","tid":2250273,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea036423a267c3a21e255b75de29b7657ae81fa","tid":2250273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0acf8af9c912f8e531a9e7e1a58da710f751c72d","tid":2250273,"uid":370061,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"佢哋當初自己報名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105579dc855805c2955d7e4c2a4e75694f8eb883","tid":2250273,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:11:47.